To sort **api tags** and **operations** in nestjs you can pass [SwaggerCustomOptions][1] to `SwaggerModule.setup()` method in following way:

      
    import { DocumentBuilder, SwaggerModule } from &#39;@nestjs/swagger&#39;;

    //...

    const config = new DocumentBuilder().addBearerAuth().build();
    const document = SwaggerModule.createDocument(app, config);
    SwaggerModule.setup(&#39;api/docs&#39;, app, document, {
      swaggerOptions: {
        apisSorter: &#39;alpha&#39;,
        tagsSorter: &#39;alpha&#39;,
        operationsSorter: &#39;alpha&#39;,
      },
    });


  [1]: https://github.com/nestjs/swagger/blob/master/lib/interfaces/swagger-custom-options.interface.ts#L5
